<h1 style="font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,38px);font-weight:400;color:#fff;margin:16px 0;line-height:1.2;">Oura Ring alternatives that require no monthly subscription</h1>
<p style="font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin-bottom:8px;">The Oura Ring is the best smart ring on the market, but its $6/month subscription puts many people off. These alternatives offer serious health tracking without any monthly fee.</p>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-family:monospace;margin-bottom:28px;">📅 {buildDate} · ⏱ 8 min read</div>
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523275335684-37898b6baf30?w=800&q=80" alt="Smart rings comparison" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;margin-bottom:28px;" loading="lazy"/>
