  <span class="verdict-box__label">⚡ QUICK CONCLUSION</span>
  <p>The Samsung Galaxy Ring and the Ultrahuman Ring Air are the best no-subscription alternatives. Samsung wins for Android users; Ultrahuman if you have an iPhone. Both cost less than the Oura and have no monthly fee.</p>
